    "More recently, the urgent call for data stewardship (Peng et al., 2021) and responsible data management practices (Stoyanovich et al., 2022) has also seen the emergence of new professional roles (Rismani & Moon, 2023).",
    "The Bias Management Layer in the NoBIAS architecture of Fig. 1 aims at achieving three main research objectives: understanding bias, mitigating bias, and accounting for bias in AI-based systems.",
